                na_if("-99")

  filter(Keying == -1) %>%
  pull(Item)

  mutate(across(c(green1:open10),
         ~ recode(.x, "1"= 0,"2" = 25, "3" = 50, "4" = 75,"5"= 100),
                .names = "{.col}_pomp"))

summary_GD <- Av_green_data_pomp %>% 
  na.omit() %>% 
  group_by(student) %>% 
  summarize(across(c(GM_pomp, IM_pomp, CM_pomp, OM_pomp),
            list(
              Av = ~ mean(.x, na.rm = T),
              SD = ~ sd(.x, na.rm = T),
              Med = ~ median(.x, na.rm = T),
              Min = ~ min(.x, na.rm = T),
              Max = ~ max(.x, na.rm = T)
            )))
